566
00:31:04,500 --> 00:31:05,220
Also,

567
00:31:07,030 --> 00:31:08,430
what did you just call me?

568
00:31:09,550 --> 00:31:10,460
Jin Zhao.

569
00:31:14,700 --> 00:31:15,590
Jin Zhao.

570
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:18,110
Jin Zhao.

571
00:31:19,180 --> 00:31:20,350
Jin Zhao.

572
00:31:21,870 --> 00:31:22,750
I've decided

573
00:31:22,880 --> 00:31:24,680
not to call you brother anymore.

574
00:31:24,820 --> 00:31:27,410
I'll just call you
by your full name, Jin Zhao.

575
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:40,040
Jiang Mu.

576
00:31:40,900 --> 00:31:42,870
Stop clinging to your brother, Jin Zhao.

577
00:31:42,870 --> 00:31:44,020
I need a partner while I practice driving.

578
00:31:44,020 --> 00:31:44,830
Do me a favor.

579
00:31:45,110 --> 00:31:46,870
Sanlai, why aren't you wearing

580
00:31:46,870 --> 00:31:48,530
your colorful clothes today?

581
00:31:48,940 --> 00:31:50,930
I'm going for a mature, steady look today,

582
00:31:50,930 --> 00:31:53,060
just changing my style occasionally.

583
00:31:54,180 --> 00:31:56,120
What did you just say? Practice driving?

584
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:56,920
That's right.

585
00:31:57,310 --> 00:31:58,070
Actually, I've always

586
00:31:58,070 --> 00:32:00,400
had a hidden identity I haven't revealed.

587
00:32:00,570 --> 00:32:01,290
What is it?

588
00:32:01,830 --> 00:32:04,350
The Racing Legend of Chinatown, known as

589
00:32:04,950 --> 00:32:06,480
Lord Sanlai of Chinatown.

590
00:32:13,860 --> 00:32:15,100
Racing Legend?

591
00:32:16,110 --> 00:32:18,310
Driving this flashy pink pickup truck?

592
00:32:18,370 --> 00:32:20,060
This isn't flashy pink.

593
00:32:20,200 --> 00:32:21,920
This is Barbie Girl pink.

594
00:32:22,130 --> 00:32:24,190
1,000 HP, 2,000 torque,

595
00:32:24,220 --> 00:32:25,050
with a Wankel engine.

596
00:32:25,050 --> 00:32:26,090
It can run even faster

597
00:32:26,090 --> 00:32:27,690
than supercars on the track.

598
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:30,750
Where are we going then?

599
00:32:30,910 --> 00:32:32,570
Let's go to the driving range.

600
00:32:32,980 --> 00:32:33,840
Are you coming?

601
00:32:38,100 --> 00:32:40,170
Of course!
Or why would I ask where we're going?

602
00:32:40,170 --> 00:32:41,180
I'll go get something.

603
00:32:41,180 --> 00:32:41,830
Okay.

604
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:19,110
Where's Sanlai?

605
00:33:19,460 --> 00:33:20,390
In the bathroom.

606
00:33:23,350 --> 00:33:25,150
Then I'll wait for him in the car.

607
00:33:27,040 --> 00:33:28,200
The key is with me.

608
00:33:41,290 --> 00:33:42,350
Give me the car key.

609
00:33:42,350 --> 00:33:43,080
She took it.

610
00:33:45,740 --> 00:33:46,540
What's wrong?

611
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:47,890
Well,

612
00:33:49,350 --> 00:33:51,430
what's with girls this age nowadays?

613
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:53,950
She was just clinging to me,

614
00:33:54,610 --> 00:33:56,320
but now she's suddenly avoiding me,

615
00:33:56,320 --> 00:33:58,250
running away faster than a rabbit.

616
00:33:58,600 --> 00:34:01,050
Hey, you're really weird.

617
00:34:01,660 --> 00:34:03,260
When everyone was going through puberty,

618
00:34:03,260 --> 00:34:04,420
you weren't interested in women.

619
00:34:04,420 --> 00:34:06,220
Now you're asking me about this?

620
00:34:06,310 --> 00:34:07,740
What are you talking about?

621
00:34:07,740 --> 00:34:08,710
What did you do to her?

622
00:34:08,710 --> 00:34:09,909
Did you bully her?

623
00:34:10,060 --> 00:34:11,790
What could I possibly do to her?

624
00:34:13,870 --> 00:34:14,909
Let me tell you.

625
00:34:15,710 --> 00:34:17,620
Don't try to guess
what women are thinking.

626
00:34:17,620 --> 00:34:19,870
You'll never figure it out anyway.

627
00:34:20,350 --> 00:34:21,230
Anyway,

628
00:34:21,420 --> 00:34:23,080
it's all because of your face.

629
00:34:23,540 --> 00:34:25,139
But I just can't accept it.

630
00:34:25,670 --> 00:34:26,670
You know, you're

631
00:34:27,060 --> 00:34:29,659
not gentle, not caring,
not even interesting.

632
00:34:29,699 --> 00:34:30,540
But why are those girls

633
00:34:30,540 --> 00:34:31,929
so eager to chase after you?

634
00:34:31,929 --> 00:34:33,139
Where do I fall short?

635
00:34:33,940 --> 00:34:35,770
Look at me from head to toe,
left to right,

636
00:34:35,770 --> 00:34:36,770
or from any angle.

637
00:34:36,770 --> 00:34:38,620
Am I not qualified to be
the campus heartthrob?

638
00:34:38,620 --> 00:34:39,820
Except for my height.

639
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:43,460
I'm going out later

640
00:34:44,980 --> 00:34:45,909
to meet someone.

641
00:34:46,980 --> 00:34:47,750
If you're free,

642
00:34:47,750 --> 00:34:49,409
send her to Jin Qiang's place,

643
00:34:50,130 --> 00:34:51,260
campus heartthrob.

644
00:34:52,659 --> 00:34:53,790
Where are you going?

645
00:34:56,409 --> 00:34:57,810
You've made up your mind?

646
00:35:01,350 --> 00:35:02,060
Got it.

647
00:35:08,850 --> 00:35:10,140
Why would Jin Zhao

648
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:12,600
buy that thing for me all of a sudden?

649
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,470
What does he mean?

650
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:18,510
Could it be that he needed it for himself

651
00:35:19,180 --> 00:35:19,980
but accidentally

652
00:35:19,980 --> 00:35:22,040
put it in the plastic bag meant for me?

653
00:35:22,580 --> 00:35:24,230
That must be it.

654
00:35:26,910 --> 00:35:28,570
Who does he want to use it with?

655
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:29,310
But

656
00:35:29,680 --> 00:35:31,230
if he has a girlfriend,

657
00:35:31,720 --> 00:35:32,910
wouldn't it be

658
00:35:32,930 --> 00:35:34,450
awkward for me to be there?

659
00:35:35,100 --> 00:35:36,100
And I couldn't

660
00:35:36,120 --> 00:35:38,290
keep going there and disrupting his life.

661
00:35:38,290 --> 00:35:40,290
It'd be inappropriate
for even a real sister,

662
00:35:40,290 --> 00:35:41,290
let alone

663
00:35:42,530 --> 00:35:45,190
someone like me
who has no blood relation to him.

664
00:35:46,860 --> 00:35:48,390
That's my alma mater, look.

665
00:35:53,900 --> 00:35:55,700
You also studied at this school?

666
00:35:56,020 --> 00:35:56,830
Yes.

667
00:35:58,580 --> 00:35:59,580
You know what?

668
00:35:59,880 --> 00:36:02,360
When I was in school,

669
00:36:02,940 --> 00:36:04,500
I was quite the big shot.

670
00:36:04,910 --> 00:36:06,390
Countless girls came to our school

671
00:36:06,390 --> 00:36:07,990
just to catch a glimpse of me.

672
00:36:08,740 --> 00:36:09,810
With this hairstyle of mine,

673
00:36:09,810 --> 00:36:12,140
I was like Manshi's Takashi Kashiwabara,

674
00:36:12,310 --> 00:36:13,910
my high school's Shun Oguri.

675
00:36:17,100 --> 00:36:18,020
No exaggeration,

676
00:36:18,020 --> 00:36:18,960
during all 3 years of high school,

677
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:20,960
I was the most handsome guy in the band.

678
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:22,820
I was just one spot away from being

679
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:24,800
the most handsome guy on campus.

680
00:36:25,290 --> 00:36:26,950
What do you mean by "one spot"?

681
00:36:27,460 --> 00:36:29,310
Well, after I registered,

682
00:36:29,500 --> 00:36:30,940
another guy came.

683
00:36:31,710 --> 00:36:33,500
He was taller than even the seniors

684
00:36:33,500 --> 00:36:35,360
and immediately
attracted everyone's attention.

685
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,510
These girls started

686
00:36:36,690 --> 00:36:38,890
spreading the word and going to see him.

687
00:36:39,380 --> 00:36:40,190
This guy was

688
00:36:41,120 --> 00:36:41,910
Brandy.

689
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:46,310
Let me tell you an interesting story.

690
00:36:46,310 --> 00:36:47,580
In high school, when most boys

691
00:36:47,580 --> 00:36:49,140
hadn't started growing taller yet,

692
00:36:49,140 --> 00:36:51,100
Brandy was already over 180 cm tall.

693
00:36:51,100 --> 00:36:52,870
During our school's cleaning days,

694
00:36:52,870 --> 00:36:53,620
for their class's cleaning,

695
00:36:53,620 --> 00:36:55,950
Brandy was always the one wiping windows.

696
00:36:56,100 --> 00:36:57,080
The most ridiculous part was

697
00:36:57,080 --> 00:36:59,460
that the class next door
would borrow him to wipe theirs.

698
00:36:59,460 --> 00:37:00,880
Whenever he went to wipe windows,

699
00:37:00,880 --> 00:37:01,880
many girls

700
00:37:02,230 --> 00:37:04,100
would poke their heads out to watch him.

701
00:37:04,100 --> 00:37:05,270
I didn't understand back then

702
00:37:05,270 --> 00:37:07,540
what was so interesting
about wiping windows.

703
00:37:07,540 --> 00:37:08,740
I only found out later

704
00:37:09,020 --> 00:37:10,350
that his uniform would ride up

705
00:37:10,350 --> 00:37:11,690
when he cleaned windows,

706
00:37:11,690 --> 00:37:13,220
so they could see his waist.

707
00:37:30,450 --> 00:37:32,230
What's so great
about seeing someone's waist?

708
00:37:32,230 --> 00:37:33,350
How would I know

709
00:37:33,350 --> 00:37:34,810
about your weird hobbies?

710
00:37:37,140 --> 00:37:37,780
By the way,

711
00:37:38,130 --> 00:37:39,770
Brandy asked me
to send you to Jin Qiang's place

712
00:37:39,770 --> 00:37:41,430
after this driving practice.

713
00:37:43,690 --> 00:37:44,610
Does Jin Zhao

714
00:37:45,150 --> 00:37:46,310
have a girlfriend?

715
00:37:48,100 --> 00:37:49,300
Well, how can I put it?

716
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:51,640
Brandy hasn't confirmed it.

717
00:37:52,290 --> 00:37:53,820
So I shouldn't say too much.

718
00:37:54,350 --> 00:37:55,140
But I can give you

719
00:37:55,140 --> 00:37:56,870
a little insider information.

720
00:37:57,140 --> 00:37:58,190
Many years ago,

721
00:37:58,250 --> 00:38:00,400
I dragged Brandy to a night market.

722
00:38:00,910 --> 00:38:02,100
After browsing around,

723
00:38:02,100 --> 00:38:03,360
I didn't buy anything,

724
00:38:03,620 --> 00:38:05,080
but he bought an ornament.

725
00:38:05,100 --> 00:38:07,160
I think the answer to your question is

726
00:38:07,350 --> 00:38:08,680
right on that ornament.

727
00:38:09,310 --> 00:38:11,390
It should be attached
to a certain key, I think.

728
00:38:11,390 --> 00:38:12,460
If you have time,

729
00:38:12,670 --> 00:38:13,600
you can go find it

730
00:38:13,720 --> 00:38:14,850
and know the answer.

731
00:38:44,770 --> 00:38:45,540
The Association's points

732
00:38:45,540 --> 00:38:48,200
stack up
based on historical race performance.

733
00:38:49,260 --> 00:38:51,540
Outsiders can hardly
make it into the rankings.

734
00:38:51,540 --> 00:38:52,580
But M-night itself is already

735
00:38:52,580 --> 00:38:53,840
awash with top racers.

736
00:38:54,270 --> 00:38:56,060
To get into the top 10

737
00:38:56,610 --> 00:38:58,580
within six months is almost impossible.

738
00:38:58,580 --> 00:39:00,040
But only racers who make it

739
00:39:00,360 --> 00:39:02,490
to the top few spots with enough points

740
00:39:03,220 --> 00:39:04,890
will get noticed by the rest.

741
00:39:05,540 --> 00:39:06,390
I did my best.

742
00:39:06,750 --> 00:39:08,210
The car isn't good enough?

743
00:39:09,140 --> 00:39:10,650
It needs major modifications.

744
00:39:10,650 --> 00:39:12,050
There's not enough time.

745
00:39:12,940 --> 00:39:14,060
Are you giving up?

746
00:39:16,910 --> 00:39:18,240
I still have two months.

747
00:39:19,270 --> 00:39:20,530
I'm going to try again.

748
00:39:21,940 --> 00:39:23,630
When will you and your team
go back to China?

749
00:39:23,630 --> 00:39:24,890
We'll stay here for now

750
00:39:25,370 --> 00:39:26,300
and wait for your good news.
